skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This flash briefing provides weekly updates about vendors and musicians at the farmers market in Washington PA. It will also feature special events throughout the summer, and identify winners of drawings and other contests.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
